dct_title_s: New York-New Jersey-Pennsylvania: Port Jervis Quadrangle
dct_description_sm: United States. Geological Survey. U.S.G.S. Alternate title: Port Jervis. Relief shown by 20 feet contour interval. Surveyed in 1884 and 1904-1906.
